<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.10">
<l>kārmali kaṇṇa puratte maṭikaḷai</l>
<l>pārmali maṅkaiyar kōṉpara kālaṉcol</l>
<l>cīrmali pāṭali vaipattum vallavar</l>
<l>nīrmali vaiyattu nīṭuniṟ pārkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten songs, where elegance abounds,</l>
<l>The words of Parakālaṉ, king of those of Maṅkai, where lands abound,</l>
<l>About our lord in Kaṇṇapuram where rain abounds,</l>
<l>They will long remain on [this] earth where water abounds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
